{"tid":741541,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"搵緊一套陳年動漫","createTime":"2018-07-13T17:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T08:59:08.000Z","uid":174493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41a1398304d9eb564797b74052b4cb6c54fe7e9b","tid":741541,"uid":174493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"故事大約係一班部隊去打會變異既人，而部隊件裝甲係黎自班異種，<br />\n<br />\n裝甲特徵：皮膚堅硬,會失控被同化<br />\n後尾班人研究到招大技可以對抗班怪物/異種，放大果陣會有類似觀音顯世/放煙花效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無記錯大台有播過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c585392fb5f64b232b337c80dbb762348a92b6","tid":741541,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"D9異形禁區"},{"pid":"ed76b7e94b326cebcccc7105d683c02f9df9cb92","tid":741541,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bc70f3e0de61f6e565364a68c687066d0bd6b91","tid":741541,"uid":174493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60c585392fb5f64b232b337c80dbb762348a92b6","tid":741541,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"D9異形禁區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce09db48448962104c55f7ac6aaa3e9020c8ce2a","tid":741541,"uid":174493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed76b7e94b326cebcccc7105d683c02f9df9cb92","tid":741541,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"偏向強殖裝甲mix最終兵器彼女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059bcdaeba5e7eebf1fc30de7ae5fc9eb5d18886","tid":741541,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"刀劍神域"},{"pid":"2521a5cd04dc757da9e0a263415ca6e3df0a8570","tid":741541,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"我都想搵套陳年動畫<br />\n<br />\n講一班人喺架太空船入面<br />\n個通風系統吸左舊隕石入去<br />\n然後變左隻怪物出嚟<br />\n有一幕係隻怪物溶左幅牆然後食左隻貓<br />\n結局係死剩一男一女棄船落左去一個星球繼續生存"}]}